Output demos/1_navigation.gif
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Macchiato"

Type "cargo run -- demos/1_navigation.json"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "lljjjj"
Sleep 500ms
Type "e"
Sleep 500ms
Type "w"
Sleep 500ms
Type "b"
Sleep 500ms
Type "]"
Sleep 500ms
Type "]"
Sleep 500ms
Type "["
Sleep 500ms
Type ":4"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type ":wq"
Enter
